OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Feasing for most, with cloud breaks
OL,7,Fdeveloping. The odd mist or fog
OL,8,Fpatches could then form, and it will
OL,9,Fbe feeling rather cool with light
OL,10,Fwinds. However, northwestern parts
OL,11,Fcould see showers continue throughout.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FShowers, perhaps merging
OL,14,Finto more persistent rain, will
OL,15,Fcontinue in the northwest. Otherwise
OL,16,Fmostly dry and fine, with variable
OL,17,Famounts of cloud. Easterly winds will
OL,18,Fgradually strengthen.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
