OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FLargely
OL,6,Ffine Sunday, with sunny spells. Band
OL,7,Fof rain clears south Monday morning,
OL,8,Ffollowed by brighter spells. Further
OL,9,Frain overnight and Tuesday morning,
OL,10,Fwith showers following.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
